Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.15,Default-JJK,Grandpa,0,0,0,,Yuji.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.19,0:00:08.95,Default-JJK,Grandpa,0,0,0,,You're a strong kid, so help people.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.65,0:00:27.67,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,109,,{\an8}In my Ten Shadows Technique,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.19,0:00:31.88,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,109,,{\an8}only two Divine Dogs are granted to the user at first.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.48,0:00:37.68,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,109,,{\an8}To use other cursed beasts, they must be subjugated.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.94,0:00:44.82,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,The user gains cursed beasts which\N they can use to subjugate more of them,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.82,0:00:49.52,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,until they command all ten cursed beasts.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.52,0:00:54.66,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,You done?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.70,0:00:59.87,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,You're really strong, just like that girl earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.87,0:01:01.17,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,And you're all still young.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.96,0:01:05.35,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,Even on your last legs,\N you give me no openings to get close.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.89,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,But with all that bleeding,\N I won't even have to do anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.71,0:01:18.85,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Thing is, this subjugation\N can be done with multiple people.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.27,0:01:25.27,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Doing so will void the ritual afterward, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.27,0:01:30.99,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Which means it becomes pointless for the sorcerer.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.07,0:01:36.99,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,But even a pointless ritual has its uses.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.75,0:01:43.37,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,Someone's being real flashy!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.09,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'll continue.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.08,0:01:52.92,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,109,,{\an8}While a cursed beast can't be used\N without subjugating it first,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.51,0:01:58.36,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,109,,{\an8}it can be summoned for the subjugation\N ritual as many times as necessary.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.89,0:01:59.77,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.61,0:02:08.57,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not a single sorcerer has ever managed to subjugate this one. {in all of sorcerer history...}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.50,0:02:13.49,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,Do you know why the Gojo clan\N and the Zenin clan are on bad terms?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.70,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,They're on bad terms?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.70,0:02:19.37,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,Sparks are {\i1}constantly{\i0} flying!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.37,0:02:22.25,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,Since the Edo Era? Or maybe Keicho?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.37,0:02:23.87,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,I forget when.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.87,0:02:29.21,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,The heads of the clans back then got serious\N during a duel before the aristocracy, {had a duel before the aristocracy} {spectated match}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.88,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,and they both died.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.51,0:02:33.38,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Were the heads of those clans...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.03,0:02:39.14,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,Just like me, one of them possessed \Nboth the Six Eyes and the Limitless technique.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.14,0:02:43.08,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,And coincidentally, the other had the same technique as you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.94,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,The Ten Shadows Technique.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.57,0:02:52.61,Default-JJK - C,Gojo,0,0,0,,You see what I'm getting at?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.36,0:02:58.28,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\i1}That doesn't mean I can become strong enough to beat you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.41,0:03:03.87,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet the head of the clan back then\N used it in much the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.38,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,With this sacred treasure, I summon...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.89,Default-JJK - C,Uraume,0,0,0,,Is something the matter, {*}Lord Sukuna{*Sukuna-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.34,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,It's urgent business.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.93,Default-JJK - C,Uraume,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.79,0:03:23.14,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,It won't be much longer before I'm free.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.38,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Do not slack on your preparations. {ah yes prepare the bath}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.20,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,See you later, Uraume.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.33,Default-JJK - C,Uraume,0,0,0,,Understood. {As you wish}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.45,Default-JJK - C,Uraume,0,0,0,,I shall be awaiting your return.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.52,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,{\i1}He got me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.98,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's starting the ritual!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.98,0:03:58.18,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he's forcing me to participate \Nin the damn thing with him!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.86,0:04:03.18,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}Eight-Handled Sword \N Divergent Sila Divine General
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.24,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Mahoraga. {its insane how that's his whole name, no commas no colon in bw}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.58,0:04:18.58,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,109,,{\fad(130,350)\an8}See you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.07,0:04:19.95,Default-JJK - C,Yuji,0,0,109,,{\fad(130,350)\an8}Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.94,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Itadori.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.95,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Hey, asshole! {let's call him what he is}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.53,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Good luck dealing with this shit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.29,Default-JJK - C,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'll see you in hell. {based megumi is so cool} {gege to the animators}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.85,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.22,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,Wait, wa-wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.23,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,Oh, fuck you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.60,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.31,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,Wake up, you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.08,0:04:58.22,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,109,,{\an8\i1}Curse user Shigemo Haruta's technique
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.22,0:05:03.57,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,109,,{\an8\i1}erases life's little daily miracles\N from his memory and stores them up. {hats off to cr for not completely messing up at least one technique explaination}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.29,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,109,,{\an8\i1}They manifest as markings under his eyes,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.29,0:05:11.08,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,109,,{\an8\i1}and a miracle is released when\N he is faced with a threat to his life.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.25,0:05:20.76,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,109,,{\an8\i1}However, he is unaware of this fact himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.89,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suspended animation, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.52,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see what's going on.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.52,0:05:37.78,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saving this piece of trash was the right move indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.21,0:05:42.66,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must have been dragged into the subjugation ritual. {he didn't "suck in" mahoraga into the ritual for subjugating mahoraga smh}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.24,0:05:49.16,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this trash dies too, the ritual will be complete,\N and Fushiguro Megumi will die as well. {Fushiguro Megumi's death will be established, as well.}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.66,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Don't die on me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.07,0:05:55.71,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,There's something I need you to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.84,Default-JJK - C,Shigemo,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.84,0:05:59.96,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.13,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order for Fushiguro Megumi to survive,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.13,0:06:08.68,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must defeat this cursed beast as an outsider,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.18,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}and nullify the subjugation ritual.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.90,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Time for a tasting, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.02,0:06:53.52,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Dismantle.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.52,0:06:53.68,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}Dismantle.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.16,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}That sword...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.79,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the Sword of Exorcism,\N specialized in combating cursed spirits.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.31,0:07:20.25,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}It carries the same positive energy\N that's generated by reverse cursed technique.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.16,0:07:27.15,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I were a cursed spirit, that would have\N eliminated me on the first hit.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.84,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Tastes awful.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.19,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,You wanna go?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.03,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.36,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,You did something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.47,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that felt odd.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.23,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.89,0:11:22.87,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cursed energy?! {according to the manga he's surprised here because the previous attacks were packed with reverse cursed energy but this one has just cursed energy} {ohh actually the rce was from sword of exorcism, not from mahoraga, which is why he's surprised that it can now attack with cursed energy}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.58,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,You really are something! {You've done it now!} {fits the context better}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.73,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,You see it, don't you? {maybe more like "recognize" (?) so he can "adapt" to it (?)} {okay he says it later}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.23,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,You can see my technique!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.20,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.10,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're like the Eight-Headed Serpent. {Yamata no Orochi}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.85,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}You recognized my slices. {follow/see through} {something feels off}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.20,0:15:57.01,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}You even started attacking with cursed energy. {ok makes sense}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.01,0:16:00.11,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both happened after that Great Wheel revolved. {not sure if it's supposed to be "great"} {it's correct since "great wheel" comes from the Great Wheel of Dharma i.e. the Wheel of Law or dharmachakra}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.96,0:16:06.61,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}The incantation of sacred treasures and the Great Wheel\N together represent a continuous cycle of balance. {furu's incantation from what i could dig up is used to bring the dead back to life (rebirth?) and the wheel represents the eightfold path to attaining enlightenment (balance?), so how does that add up to cycles and harmony? and more importantly how does that hint at the ability to adapt?} {a more sensible reading would be the wheel representing overcoming of obstacles which would be right in line with mahoraga's ability} {nah this is fine if you think of it as a continuous cycle of balance}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.61,0:16:13.22,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which suggests that this cursed beast's ability\N is to adapt to anything and everything. {so as to maintain that cycle of balance}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.83,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the ultimate late-throw rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.20,0:16:22.83,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,682)\i1}You might have defeated me in the state I was in back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.81,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Well, you showed me, Fushiguro Megumi! {reply to his line back in 05: show me what you've got, Fushiguro Megumi!}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.23,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,235)}Domain Expansion:
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.06,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Malevolent Shrine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.06,0:16:40.15,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\iclip(775,868,1142,960)}Malevolent Shrine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.63,0:16:51.45,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Sukuna's Domain, Malevolent Shrine, is a curious one.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.46,0:16:57.41,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Unlike other domains, it does not\N close its barrier to cut out a separate space.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.95,0:17:06.17,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Manifesting an innate domain without closing its barrier \N is like painting an art piece not on a canvas but in the air.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.13,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}It is truly a divine feat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.43,0:17:14.68,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Additionally, allowing its victims a\N path of escape acts as a Binding Vow
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.68,0:17:21.05,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}which vastly increases the range of its sure-hit\N effect to a maximum radius of 200 meters.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.70,0:17:25.59,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Out of consideration for Fushiguro Megumi,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.59,0:17:31.45,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}he has currently limited that effect to a 140 meter radius.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.99,Default-JJK - C,Keiko,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.67,Default-JJK - C,A,0,0,0,,Nope. No signal.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.46,Default-JJK - C,Keiko,0,0,0,,Same.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.04,0:17:52.46,Default-JJK - C,A,0,0,0,,I don't think we need to worry too much, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.46,0:17:52.97,Default-JJK - C,Keiko,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.80,Default-JJK - C,A,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(1110,2110,\bord5\blur8)}Remember the guy with the megaphone? {He should be---} {idk why this was here}
Dialogue: 11,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.80,Default-JJK - C,A,0,0,0,,{\bord0\t(1110,2110,\blur5)}Remember the guy with the megaphone? {He should be---} {idk why this was here}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.02,0:18:01.79,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Sukuna's slices are comprised of two types.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.79,0:18:06.91,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Within the range of his sure-hit effect,\N Cleave attacks objects that possess cursed energy,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.91,0:18:09.48,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}while Dismantle attacks objects that do not.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.20,0:18:14.41,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Both rain down endlessly upon everything\N until Malevolent Shrine disappears.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.91,0:18:19.17,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}There is only one guaranteed way to defeat Mahoraga:
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.17,0:18:23.09,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Annihilate it with a new attack before it can adapt to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.64,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Cleave would have fulfilled those conditions,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.64,0:18:32.01,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}but rather than adapting just to Dismantle,\Nif it had adapted to slices in general,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.61,0:18:35.32,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}that would be a different story entirely. {that wouldn't necessarily hold true.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.96,0:18:57.82,Default-JJK - C,Narrator,0,0,114,,{\an8\i1}Mahoraga was close to finishing its regeneration.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.31,Default-JJK - C,Sukuna,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Open.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.33,Default-JJK,Sukuna,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.66,Default-JJK,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Begone.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.06,0:20:32.63,Default-JJK,Shigemo,0,0,0,,E-E-Excuse me, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.25,Default-JJK,Shigemo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really am lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.71,0:20:36.88,Default-JJK,Shigemo,0,0,0,,{\i1}For another day...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.26,Default-JJK,Shigemo,0,0,0,,I survived!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.01,0:20:47.52,Default-JJK,Narrator,0,0,42,,{\an8\i1}Shigemo's stock of miracles had been\N exhausted in his battle with Nanami Kento.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.15,Default-JJK,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Oh, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.58,0:20:57.71,Default-JJK,Yaga,0,0,0,,Fushiguro!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.87,Default-JJK,Yaga,0,0,42,,{\i1\an8}I think I saw Itadori for a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.49,Default-JJK,Yaga,0,0,42,,{\i1\an8}No, was it Sukuna?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.54,0:21:16.38,Default-JJK,Sukuna,0,0,0,,Hey, brat, be sure to savor this.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.02,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,I should've died.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.57,0:22:05.23,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,I was supposed to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.50,0:22:08.38,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,It should've been me! {i should kms for this}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.56,0:22:10.73,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,Just kill yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.78,0:22:13.14,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.15,0:23:14.36,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get up.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.37,0:23:17.88,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.98,0:23:28.73,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.07,0:23:32.97,Default-JJK,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm nothing but a murderer.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.80,Default-JJK,Panda,0,0,42,,{\an8}Things are really getting out of hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.80,0:23:56.96,Default-JJK,Panda,0,0,42,,{\an8}I'll count prime numbers to calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.96,0:24:00.29,Default-JJK,Panda,0,0,42,,{\an8}One, two, three... uh, nine...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.29,0:24:01.78,Default-JJK,Kusakabe,0,0,42,,{\an8}You missed five and seven.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.78,0:24:02.83,Default-JJK,Panda,0,0,42,,{\an8}Next time, Right and Wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.83,0:24:04.64,Default-JJK,Panda,0,0,42,,{\an8}You'll turn into a panda if you don't watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.64,0:24:06.62,Default-JJK,Kusakabe,0,0,42,,{\an8}You really are an animal.
